跟「義大利」家庭
and an "Italian" family.

877
00:58:41,275 --> 00:58:44,237
所以家裡禁止說西語
So he disallows Spanish in his home.

878
00:58:45,029 --> 00:58:48,533
他跟她家人斷絕往來
He cuts off contact with her family.

879
00:58:48,783 --> 00:58:50,619
我媽什麼都沒有
My mother has nothing.

880
00:58:51,828 --> 00:58:53,663
她沒有人可以愛
No one to love.

881
00:58:55,374 --> 00:58:57,376
於是她想辦法懷孕
And so she gets pregnant.

882
00:58:57,917 --> 00:58:59,336
懷了我
With me.

883
00:59:07,260 --> 00:59:08,803
我長大一些以後
As I get older...

884
00:59:08,970 --> 00:59:12,641
只要我爸去出差
whenever my father travels for work,

885
00:59:12,641 --> 00:59:17,604
她就會找人從家鄉寄包裹來
she arranges packages to be sent from home.

886
00:59:17,604 --> 00:59:20,314
西班牙食物、葡萄酒
Spanish foods, wines.

887
00:59:20,565 --> 00:59:22,359
我們最愛的是
Our favorite treat was

888
00:59:22,359 --> 00:59:29,949
西班牙橄欖油，你想得到嗎？
the Spanish olive oil. Can you imagine?

889
00:59:29,991 --> 00:59:33,537
我們在義大利鄉間
There we are in the Italian countryside,

890
00:59:33,703 --> 00:59:37,331
舉世最聞名的橄欖油產地
home to the most famous olive oil in the world,

891
00:59:38,124 --> 00:59:41,002
狂吞西班牙橄欖油
pouring Spanish olive oil down our throats

892
00:59:41,002 --> 00:59:44,506
就像我們現在喝曼查尼亞一樣
like we now drink this manzanilla.

893
00:59:46,883 --> 00:59:50,679
我跟我媽是一對寶
What a pair Mama and I were.

894
00:59:53,264 --> 00:59:54,558
一對寶
What a pair.

895
01:00:00,605 --> 01:00:04,317
我媽在我16歲時就過世了
She died, my mother, when I was just 16.

896
01:00:05,819 --> 01:00:08,613
她一過世
As soon as she died,

897
01:00:08,613 --> 01:00:10,824
那混蛋貴族立刻跟我切斷
that royal fuck of a man cut me off.

898
01:00:12,617 --> 01:00:15,912
他在我身上看到我媽的影子
He saw my mother in me.

899
01:00:16,120 --> 01:00:18,122
而他在我媽身上只看到
And in my mother he saw only

900
01:00:18,122 --> 01:00:20,625
一個低賤的西班牙人毀了他的人生
a dirty Spaniard who had ruined his life.

901
01:00:24,588 --> 01:00:26,047
幸虧
But luckily for me...

902
01:00:30,469 --> 01:00:33,262
我爸不只頑固
my father wasn't just a bigot,

903
01:00:34,473 --> 01:00:36,475
他還很自戀
he was also a narcissist.

904
01:00:37,434 --> 01:00:38,768
他從來沒想過自己會死
He never thought he would die,

905
01:00:38,768 --> 01:00:42,356
就算他年紀大了、常生病也一樣
even as he got older, even as he got sicker.

906
01:00:43,773 --> 01:00:47,819
所以，他根本沒立遺囑
And so... he never made a will.

907
01:00:51,948 --> 01:00:54,409
他一離開人世後
The moment he left this earth,

908
01:00:55,660 --> 01:00:59,373
我就成了超級富豪，哈維耶
I became a wildly wealthy man, Javier.

909
01:01:03,001 --> 01:01:06,463
我馬上購回安達魯西亞這塊地
And the first thing I did was buy this land
back in Andalusia,

910
01:01:06,463 --> 01:01:09,257
現在我有大片土地
where I now grow hundreds of acres

911
01:01:09,257 --> 01:01:13,177
能釀造我跟我媽當初囤積的橄欖油
of the olive oil that Mama and I once hoarded.

912
01:01:14,596 --> 01:01:20,309
雖然我為了事業多半時候不在
And while… business keeps me away most of the time,

913
01:01:21,185 --> 01:01:24,230
但我只重視這片土地
this land is the only thing that matters to me.

914
01:01:27,567 --> 01:01:31,738
這片土地是我跟我媽的故事
This land is my story, and it is my mama's story.

915
01:01:35,033 --> 01:01:36,618
這就是為什麼…
That is why...

916
01:01:38,412 --> 01:01:40,329
橄欖…
the olives...

917
01:01:41,665 --> 01:01:43,458
對我來說很重要
mean so much to me.

918
01:01:48,171 --> 01:01:49,381
現在
And now...

919
01:01:50,173 --> 01:01:51,675
我得問你
I must ask:

920
01:01:53,843 --> 01:01:56,262
橄欖對你的重要性是什麼？
Why do they mean so much to you?

921
01:02:00,559 --> 01:02:02,352
我不懂你的意思
I don't follow, sir.

922
01:02:04,646 --> 01:02:08,274
其他工人用耙子跟網子採收
The other men use rakes and nets,

923
01:02:08,274 --> 01:02:10,276
你卻是手摘
but you pick by hand.

924
01:02:11,152 --> 01:02:13,738
你手摘的產量只有一半
You can only pick half as many.

925
01:02:14,698 --> 01:02:16,324
所以我的工時是兩倍
That's why I work twice as long.

926
01:02:16,324 --> 01:02:17,451
不，這點我知道
No, I am aware.

927
01:02:17,451 --> 01:02:20,244
我不是指責你，我是純粹想問你
This is not criticism. It is simply a question.

928
01:02:21,245 --> 01:02:23,707
你為什麼比其他工人認真做事？
Why do you work harder than the other men?

929
01:02:25,417 --> 01:02:27,711
因為這是正確的做法
Because it's the right way.

930
01:02:29,963 --> 01:02:33,633
我跟你說了我的故事
I tell you my story,

931
01:02:33,758 --> 01:02:36,761
說了我的混蛋老爸
the story of my fuck of a father

932
01:02:36,761 --> 01:02:40,515
我可憐受虐的媽媽，而我反問你時
and my poor abused mother,
and when I ask you for the same,

933
01:02:40,515 --> 01:02:43,810
你卻只回答我這一句話？
all I get is "because it's the right way?"

934
01:02:47,230 --> 01:02:50,650
快喝你的酒，說說你的故事吧
Come on, drink your manzanilla and tell me your story.

935
01:02:59,075 --> 01:03:02,454
我是簡單的人，沒有值得提的事
I am a simple man. I do not have a story.

936
01:03:03,747 --> 01:03:06,332
我沒有混蛋老爸
I did not have a fuck of a father.

937
01:03:07,000 --> 01:03:11,463
我爸很風趣，會邊工作邊吹口哨
My father was funny and whistled while he worked.

938
01:03:13,131 --> 01:03:16,635
我也喜歡能邊吹口哨的工作
And I like having a job
where I can whistle while I work, too.

939
01:03:20,096 --> 01:03:22,682
耙子會弄傷橄欖
The rakes bruise the olives...

940
01:03:24,225 --> 01:03:26,310
所以我才用手摘
so I pick them by hand.

941
01:03:27,061 --> 01:03:29,398
這是正確的做法，就這樣
It's the right way. That is all.

942
01:03:36,446 --> 01:03:38,532
工人愛戴你
The men love you.

943
01:03:39,574 --> 01:03:43,912
我聽說你會說故事逗他們開心
I hear you telling them stories, making them laugh.

944
01:03:44,871 --> 01:03:49,000
我愛說話　-但你面對我卻很拘謹
- I have a big mouth. - But with me, you are reserved.

945
01:03:49,501 --> 01:03:51,378
你是我的老闆
You are my boss.

946
01:03:51,670 --> 01:03:53,296
我想跟你當朋友
I want to be your friend.

947
01:03:54,881 --> 01:03:55,840
不要
No.

948
01:03:58,051 --> 01:03:59,886
我當朋友會讓你失望
I would disappoint you as your friend.

949
01:04:00,136 --> 01:04:02,889
才不會
I disagree. I disagree.

950
01:04:03,139 --> 01:04:05,058
我回答你了
I gave you my answer.

951
01:04:15,902 --> 01:04:19,489
有意思，很多人欣賞我
It's curious. The other men admire me,

952
01:04:19,531 --> 01:04:23,117
他們幾乎不了解我
and they barely know me.

953
01:04:23,660 --> 01:04:26,538
而你聽完我的故事後卻無動於衷
But you, you hear my story and it does not affect you.

954
01:04:28,164 --> 01:04:30,917
這件事不會讓你…
It does not make you...

955
01:04:31,376 --> 01:04:32,919
欣賞我嗎？
like me?

956
01:04:33,962 --> 01:04:39,634
沒關係，你老實說就行了
It's okay, you can be completely honest.

957
01:04:41,553 --> 01:04:43,680
這不會讓我欣賞你
No, it does not.

958
01:04:47,100 --> 01:04:48,810
我可以問原因嗎？
May I ask why?

959
01:04:52,564 --> 01:04:54,524
要是我就不會拿你爸的錢
I would not have taken his money.

960
01:05:08,372 --> 01:05:09,330
好
Okay.

961
01:05:11,458 --> 01:05:13,084
你想住在這裡
Would you like to live here

962
01:05:14,085 --> 01:05:17,381
當工頭監督工人嗎？
and oversee the men as foreman?

963
01:05:18,757 --> 01:05:19,924
免費嗎？
For free?

964
01:05:20,759 --> 01:05:22,511
對，免費
Yes, for free.

965
01:05:22,802 --> 01:05:25,430
我當然還會替你加薪
Of course, there would be a raise.

966
01:05:25,597 --> 01:05:29,183
不用，免房租已經夠好了
No. The free rent would be more than enough.

967
01:05:29,183 --> 01:05:30,727
可是我有一個條件
But I have one condition.

968
01:05:32,311 --> 01:05:33,855
我會管理好你的土地
I will take care of your land.

969
01:05:35,440 --> 01:05:38,276
會當成自己的好好經營
I will help it thrive as if it's my own.

970
01:05:41,237 --> 01:05:43,698
但我不會為你吹口哨
But my whistling is for me,

971
01:05:46,368 --> 01:05:48,703
我愛說話只留給工人
and my big mouth is for the men.

972
01:05:51,581 --> 01:05:53,417
你不能對我做出這種要求
You will not ask of that from me.

973
01:05:54,543 --> 01:05:57,421
我也不會開口要求你任何事
And I will never ask anything of you.

974
01:06:06,596 --> 01:06:10,058
<i>就在這時候，在不遠的4千哩外</i>

975
