How do you say it so calmly?

1022
01:09:11,740 --> 01:09:13,783
恭喜
Congratulations!

1023
01:09:14,993 --> 01:09:16,786
恭喜
Congratulations!

1024
01:09:17,412 --> 01:09:19,873
