I can make a life for us now.

1025
01:09:21,916 --> 01:09:23,209
貝兒
Bella...

1026
01:09:24,336 --> 01:09:26,463
我知道我永遠不會大富大貴
I know I'll never be a rich man.

1027
01:09:26,755 --> 01:09:29,173
